    <item>
      <title>Design Overview</title>
      <link>https://gsi-hpc.github.io/sind/next/architecture/overview/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://gsi-hpc.github.io/sind/next/architecture/overview/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;flex align-center gdoc-page__anchorwrap&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h2 id=&#34;one-shot-not-reconciling&#34;&#xA;    &gt;&#xA;        One-shot, not reconciling&#xA;    &lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;    &lt;a data-clipboard-text=&#34;https://gsi-hpc.github.io/sind/next/architecture/overview/#one-shot-not-reconciling&#34; class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchor clip flex align-center&#34; title=&#34;Anchor to: One-shot, not reconciling&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor to: One-shot, not reconciling&#34; href=&#34;#one-shot-not-reconciling&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;svg class=&#34;gdoc-icon gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;use xlink:href=&#34;#gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;While the cluster configuration resembles a Kubernetes manifest, sind is &lt;strong&gt;not&lt;/strong&gt; a reconciling controller. The configuration is a one-shot input:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;sind create cluster&lt;/code&gt; interprets the manifest once to generate the cluster&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;sind does not watch or reconcile cluster state&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;sind does not automatically repair drift or failures&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;sind provides commands for inspection (&lt;code&gt;get&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;status&lt;/code&gt;), modification (&lt;code&gt;create/delete worker&lt;/code&gt;), and simulation (&lt;code&gt;power&lt;/code&gt;), but these are imperative operations, not declarative state management.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Networking</title>
      <link>https://gsi-hpc.github.io/sind/next/architecture/networking/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://gsi-hpc.github.io/sind/next/architecture/networking/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;flex align-center gdoc-page__anchorwrap&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h2 id=&#34;cluster-network&#34;&#xA;    &gt;&#xA;        Cluster network&#xA;    &lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;    &lt;a data-clipboard-text=&#34;https://gsi-hpc.github.io/sind/next/architecture/networking/#cluster-network&#34; class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchor clip flex align-center&#34; title=&#34;Anchor to: Cluster network&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor to: Cluster network&#34; href=&#34;#cluster-network&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;svg class=&#34;gdoc-icon gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;use xlink:href=&#34;#gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Each cluster has an isolated Docker bridge network:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Name: &lt;code&gt;sind-&amp;lt;cluster&amp;gt;-net&lt;/code&gt; (e.g., &lt;code&gt;sind-dev-net&lt;/code&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Nodes can reach each other by container hostname within this network&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;flex align-center gdoc-page__anchorwrap&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h2 id=&#34;mesh-network&#34;&#xA;    &gt;&#xA;        Mesh network&#xA;    &lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;    &lt;a data-clipboard-text=&#34;https://gsi-hpc.github.io/sind/next/architecture/networking/#mesh-network&#34; class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchor clip flex align-center&#34; title=&#34;Anchor to: Mesh network&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor to: Mesh network&#34; href=&#34;#mesh-network&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;svg class=&#34;gdoc-icon gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;use xlink:href=&#34;#gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;All clusters join a shared mesh network for cross-cluster communication:&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Docker Resources</title>
      <link>https://gsi-hpc.github.io/sind/next/architecture/docker-resources/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://gsi-hpc.github.io/sind/next/architecture/docker-resources/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;flex align-center gdoc-page__anchorwrap&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h2 id=&#34;per-cluster-resources&#34;&#xA;    &gt;&#xA;        Per-cluster resources&#xA;    &lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;    &lt;a data-clipboard-text=&#34;https://gsi-hpc.github.io/sind/next/architecture/docker-resources/#per-cluster-resources&#34; class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchor clip flex align-center&#34; title=&#34;Anchor to: Per-cluster resources&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor to: Per-cluster resources&#34; href=&#34;#per-cluster-resources&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;svg class=&#34;gdoc-icon gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;use xlink:href=&#34;#gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;table&gt;&#xA;  &lt;thead&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;th&gt;Type&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;          &lt;th&gt;Name pattern&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;          &lt;th&gt;Example (&lt;code&gt;sind create cluster dev&lt;/code&gt;)&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/thead&gt;&#xA;  &lt;tbody&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;Network&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;&amp;lt;realm&amp;gt;-&amp;lt;cluster&amp;gt;-net&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;sind-dev-net&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;Controller&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;&amp;lt;realm&amp;gt;-&amp;lt;cluster&amp;gt;-controller&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;sind-dev-controller&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;Submitter&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;&amp;lt;realm&amp;gt;-&amp;lt;cluster&amp;gt;-submitter&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;sind-dev-submitter&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;Worker&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;&amp;lt;realm&amp;gt;-&amp;lt;cluster&amp;gt;-worker-&amp;lt;N&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;sind-dev-worker-0&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;Config volume&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;&amp;lt;realm&amp;gt;-&amp;lt;cluster&amp;gt;-config&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;sind-dev-config&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;Munge volume&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;&amp;lt;realm&amp;gt;-&amp;lt;cluster&amp;gt;-munge&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;sind-dev-munge&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;Data volume&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;&amp;lt;realm&amp;gt;-&amp;lt;cluster&amp;gt;-data&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;sind-dev-data&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/tbody&gt;&#xA;&lt;/table&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The default realm is &lt;code&gt;sind&lt;/code&gt; and the default cluster name is &lt;code&gt;default&lt;/code&gt;, resulting in prefixes like &lt;code&gt;sind-default-*&lt;/code&gt;. See &lt;a&#xA;  class=&#34;gdoc-markdown__link&#34;&#xA;  href=&#34;../../configuration/realms/&#34;&#xA;&gt;Realms&lt;/a&gt; for custom realm naming.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Slurm Configuration</title>
      <link>https://gsi-hpc.github.io/sind/next/architecture/slurm-config/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://gsi-hpc.github.io/sind/next/architecture/slurm-config/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;flex align-center gdoc-page__anchorwrap&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h2 id=&#34;generated-files&#34;&#xA;    &gt;&#xA;        Generated files&#xA;    &lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;    &lt;a data-clipboard-text=&#34;https://gsi-hpc.github.io/sind/next/architecture/slurm-config/#generated-files&#34; class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchor clip flex align-center&#34; title=&#34;Anchor to: Generated files&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor to: Generated files&#34; href=&#34;#generated-files&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;svg class=&#34;gdoc-icon gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;use xlink:href=&#34;#gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;sind generates a multi-file Slurm configuration and writes it to the &lt;code&gt;sind-&amp;lt;cluster&amp;gt;-config&lt;/code&gt; volume:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;/etc/slurm/&#xA;├── slurm.conf              # main config&#xA;├── sind-nodes.conf         # sind-managed node definitions&#xA;├── cgroup.conf             # cgroupv2 configuration&#xA;├── plugstack.conf          # SPANK plugin config (always created)&#xA;├── plugstack.conf.d/       # SPANK plugin fragments (always created)&#xA;├── slurm.conf.d/           # main config fragments (if slurm.main is a map)&#xA;├── cgroup.conf.d/          # cgroup fragments (if slurm.cgroup is a map)&#xA;├── gres.conf               # generic resources (if slurm.gres is set)&#xA;└── topology.conf           # network topology (if slurm.topology is set)&#xA;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;flex align-center gdoc-page__anchorwrap&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h2 id=&#34;slurmconf&#34;&#xA;    &gt;&#xA;        slurm.conf&#xA;    &lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;    &lt;a data-clipboard-text=&#34;https://gsi-hpc.github.io/sind/next/architecture/slurm-config/#slurmconf&#34; class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchor clip flex align-center&#34; title=&#34;Anchor to: slurm.conf&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor to: slurm.conf&#34; href=&#34;#slurmconf&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;svg class=&#34;gdoc-icon gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;use xlink:href=&#34;#gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The main configuration file includes cluster name, controller host, process tracking settings, and always contains:&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
